      "title": "Distribution & Sales: CAA imposes strict conditions on series of goods",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Consumer Affairs Authority issued an extraordinary gazette with regard to the distribution, and sale, of 37 goods to the local market.",
        "The CAA said the gazette was issued to strramline the supply, and distribution of goods to the market.",
        "Distribution & Sales: CAA imposes strict conditions on series of goods"
